==Hishimochi Quests==
A seasonal quest chain (2 quests) were added for the mochi. It was reported that [[Quest#B6|Quest B6]] needs to be clear to unlock the first quest.

[[File:Aaa.jpg|300px|center]]

The first quest (shown above) requires 3 mochi to complete. This rewards:
*Resources: 330 {{ammo}} & 330 {{steel}}
*One [[File:Furniture_box_large.jpg]] Large furniture box
*One [[File:Furniture_fairy.png]] Furniture fairy
[[File:2nd_mochi_quest.png|300px|center]]

The 2nd quest (shown above) requires 10 mochi to complete and rewards:
*Resources: 880 {{ammo}} & 880 {{steel}}
*One [[File:Food_set.jpg]] Food Supply Ship Mamiya
*One [[Skilled Lookouts]]
<p style="margin-bottom:1em;color:rgb(0,0,0);">'''Note:'''</p>

<p style="margin-bottom:1em;color:rgb(0,0,0);">Mochi Quests count what you '''have'''. You '''only need to get 10 mochis''' to complete 1st and 2nd quest. Therefore, it is advised not use any of the mochi until you have completed the chain quest to avoid having to find more mochi.</p>

